Free payments in tenge and volumes for replenishment and withdrawal of cash are valid until the next commission write-off for the package. The validity date of the package can be viewed on the My Package screen. Commissions for operations that are not indicated in the "Collect Your Package" or are not included in the package are written off at the "Standard tariffs. 

If there are not enough payments in the package until the next renewal of the package, you can buy a one-time additional package. Click on the icon > and buy the quantity you need. Additional payments the package will be carried over after the main package is renewed. The same goes for deposits and withdrawals. 

You can also enable and disable discounts for transfers in rubles and foreign currencies without changing the main package. The commission for connecting the discount will be recalculated taking into account the remaining time of the package.
All additional card accounts are linked to the main card account of the Company

First, the volumes of deposits and withdrawals are spent on the main package, after they are completed, they will begin to be spent on the additional one. \nTo buy another additional package, you must spend the previously purchased one.

An additional package is available immediately after connection. When extending the main package, unused volumes of replenishment and withdrawal of the additional package are transferred to the next month. When the main package is turned off, all unused deposits and withdrawals are burned out. Several additional packages cannot be purchased at the same time, the next one will be available after using the first one.

First, payments are spent on the main package, after their completion, they will begin to be spent on an additional one. \nTo buy another additional package, you must spend the previously purchased one.

An additional package is available immediately after connection. When renewing the main package, unused payments of the additional package are carried over to the next month. When you disable the main package, all unused payments are burned. \nSeveral additional packages cannot be purchased at the same time, the next one will be available after using the first one.

From 1 000 to 40 000 tenge per month - depending on the chosen services. Payment is debited immediately after connection and then monthly on the same date.
